		<div id="comment_body_64515849">The negatives cited in the summary all sound either very hypothetical or niche cases. For the majority, if you are able to complete the work you're assigned, what does it matter where you are? Sounds like just another case of those wanting to micromanage their direct reports and justify their own job.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64515849">
